title: Eps. 105 - Stop, Drop, and Roll
description:
This week on the podcast the guys are back from celebrating the holiday season with a special guest. Jamal King who’s had dreams of being a millionaire since he was a kid. Jamal tells his story of growing up in Chicago in a blue collar family. His story starts with him becoming a Chicago cop to now a successful entrepreneur who’s made his dreams of being a millionaire come true. One of the key things Jamal mentions is that his exposure to a different way of life is what allowed him to believe he can obtain it. Whatever your vision is for your life find a way to get exposed to it.
